      "questionText": "<p>Given below are two statements:</p>\n<p>Statement - I: High concentration of strong nucleophilic reagent with secondary alkyl halides which do not have bulky substituents will follow $$\\mathrm{S}_{\\mathrm{N}}{ }^2$$ mechanism.</p>\n<p>Statement - II: A secondary alkyl halide when treated with a large excess of ethanol follows $$\\mathrm{S}_{\\mathrm{N}}{ }^1$$ mechanism.</p>\n<p>In the light of the above statements, choose the most appropriate from the options given below:</p>",
      "options": [
